            <h3 style="margin-right:10px; color:#50A2D4;border-bottom:1px solid #50A2D4;"><strong>How to type in Geez?</strong> </h3> 
            <div>
               <p> 
                    1) Press the root key (refer the key map for all English to geez conversion), lets try "h" as an example
               </p>
               <p style="">
                    <a class="key">h</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሀ</a>
               </p>
               <p>
                2) If that is the geez letter you were looking for then great! But if you want to
                   modify it to the other sounds of the same root category, press any one of the modifier
                   keys. Like in the example below.
               </p>
               <p style="">
                    <a class="key">u</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሁ</a>
                 </p>
                 <p>
                    <a class="key">i&nbsp</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሂ</a>
                </p>
                 <p>
                    <a class="key">a</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሃ</a>
                </p>
                 <p>
                    <a class="key">y</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሄ</a>
                </p>
                 <p>
                    <a class="key">e</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ህ</a>
                </p>
                 <p>
                    <a class="key">o</a>
                    you should see 
                    <a class="typing geeztext">ሆ</a>
               </p>
               <p>
               3) And that is it , as a reminder the root can also be a combination of one english letter
                and/or shift or caps keys
               </p>
            </div>
        </div>
